title: Tanias 33 Dos Mundos
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Fast food, Take-out, Mexican, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Typcial little Mexican burrito joint but for a large selection of vegetarian dishes. As the sign says, not just bean/cheese burritos here: vegan calabacitas, soy chorizo, soy machaca, soy verde, and rice-based horchata. Makes its own tortillas and corn chips.
